nala, čitav proces ostaje nevidljiv"},"tags":["future-pulse","automated","space"],"geo":{"name":"Menlo Park, CA","lat":37.4529,"lon":-122.1817,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$20","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-16-perovskites-quiet-leap-why-flexible-solar-cells-ma","title":"Perovskit u svemiru: zašto fleksibilni paneli mijenjaju igru","category":"space","date":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada se razmišlja o opskrbi energijom u svemiru, tradicionalni solarni paneli predstavljaju paradoks: pouzdani su, ali kruti, teški i nepraktični za misije gdje svaki gram broji.","execSummary":"TNO’s Perovion Technologies is betting on roll-to-roll perovskite solar cells to solve a critical space challenge: lightweight, flexible power for missions where rigid panels fail. The 2030 factory plan isn’t just industrial scaling—it’s a test of whether perovskite can endure space’s harsh conditions, with implications for lunar bases, long-duration satellites, and the broader shift toward in-situ resource utilization.","source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/perovskites-quiet-leap-why-flexible-solar-cells-ma/main.jpg","alt":"Perovskit u svemiru: zašto fleksibilni paneli mijenjaju igru"},"subtitle":"Kad je Sunčeva svjetlost resurs, a težina neprijatelj — perovskit postaje ključni saveznik","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/perovskites-quiet-leap-why-flexible-solar-cells-ma/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kad je Sunčeva svjetlost resurs, a težina neprijatelj — perovskit postaje ključni saveznik"},"tags":["Perovskite","Solar Panels","Space Exploration"],"geo":{"name":"Eindhoven, Netherlands","lat":51.4416,"lon":5.4697,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$21","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-16-senate-mandates-a-moon-base-nasa-s-2030-deadline-g","title":"NASA-in lunarni dom do 2030.: Zašto je to ključni korak za duboki svemir","category":"space","date":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","sc