anje’ može promijeniti pravila igre u AI sigurnosti","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/reasoning-based-llm-unlearning-targets-model-safet/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Od gradientnih metoda do rasuđivanja: zašto ‘pametno zaboravljanje’ može promijeniti pravila igre u AI sigurnosti"},"tags":["future-pulse","automated","space"],"geo":{"name":"Menlo Park, CA","lat":37.4529,"lon":-122.1817,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$27","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-11-cyber-and-space-the-pentagons-quiet-first-move-pla","title":"Cyber i svemir: Pentagonovi prvi potezi protiv Irana","category":"space","date":"2026-03-11T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-11T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Pentagon je po prvi put detaljnije objavio kako su U.","source":{"name":"Future Pulse","url":"https://futurepulse.hr"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/cyber-and-space-the-pentagons-quiet-first-move-pla/main.jpg","alt":"Cyber i svemir: Pentagonovi prvi potezi protiv Irana"},"subtitle":"Što znače 'kontinuirano složeni učinci' za industriju i korisnike?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/cyber-and-space-the-pentagons-quiet-first-move-pla/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što znače 'kontinuirano složeni učinci' za industriju i korisnike?"},"tags":["future-pulse","automated","space"],"geo":{"name":"Iran","lat":32.427908,"lon":53.688046,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$28","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-11-nasa-detects-a-star-collision-where-none-should-ex","title":"NASA otkriva rijetku sudaru zvijezda – zašto je ovo ključno za kozmologiju?","category":"space","date":"2026-03-11T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-11T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada se dvije ultra-guste zvijezde – vjerojatno neutronske zvijezde – sudare u malenoj galaktici utrnutoj u divovskom plinskom toku, to nije samo spektakl.","source":{"name":"Future Pulse","url":"https://futurepulse.hr"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/nasa-detects-a-star-collision-where-none-should-ex/main.jpg","alt":"NASA